        {
            "paragraph": 5,
            "sentence_id": 10,
            "sentence_md5": "491bf4e04183630acf21eebadcb80048",
            "sentence": "“Gift receivers would be happier if givers gave them exactly what they requested rather than attempting to be ‘thoughtful and considerate’ by buying gifts they did not explicitly request” to surprise them, the researchers write.",
            "phonetic": "/ɡɪft rɪˈsivərz wʊd bi ˈhæpiər ɪf ˈɡɪvərz ɡeɪv ðəm ɪgˈzæktli wɒt ðeɪ rɪˈkwɛstɪd ˈræðər ðæn əˈtɛmptɪŋ tu bi ˈθɔtfəl ænd kənˈsɪdərət baɪ ˈbaɪɪŋ ɡɪfts ðeɪ dɪd nɑt ɪkˈsplɪsɪtli rɪˈkwɛst tu sərˈpraɪz ðəm ðə rɪˈsɜrʧərz raɪt/",
            "translation": "研究人员写道：“如果送礼者给他们正是他们要求的东西，而不是试图通过购买他们没有明确要求的礼物来‘体贴周到’地给他们惊喜，收礼者会更高兴。”",
